    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior shows a nice shine, though you may find a few minor stone chips and light surface scratches upon close inspection. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, showing only normal wear on the seating surfaces. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and has a documented service history, making it a reliable choice for its next owner.",
